curam.util.ctm.bom.resources.impl

Class XMLAppResourceInformationalBOMImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.ctm.bom.BusinessObjectModuleImpl
      • curam.util.ctm.bom.resources.impl.AppResourceInformationalBOMImpl
        • curam.util.ctm.bom.resources.impl.XMLAppResourceInformationalBOMImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BusinessObjectModule, InformationalBOM

    public class XMLAppResourceInformationalBOMImpl
extends AppResourceInformationalBOMImpl
    This is the Informational Business Object Module implementation for an AppResource BOM. A resource BOM consists of the resource in the specified locale, or any locale if none is specified. This class will give information about existing resources.
